118
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:21,820
[Amor Aeternus]

119
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,150
What does it mean?

120
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:27,600
Loving you

121
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:28,750
every day.

122
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,440
So mushy.

123
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,320
People might mistake this
for a proposal.

124
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,000
