125
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:45,120
I'm not actually proposing?

126
00:10:57,100 --> 00:11:00,180
[Amor Aeternus]

127
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,200
Hello?

128
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,320
Hello?

129
00:11:14,870 --> 00:11:15,600
It's me,

130
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:16,960
Liao Jinyuan.

131
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,200
How are you?

132
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:23,790
I don't mean anything.

133
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:26,360
It's maybe because I had a bit to drink.

134
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:29,080
I want to see you.

135
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,000
Just as an old friend.

136
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:33,870
Your old friend died three years ago.

137
00:11:37,670 --> 00:11:38,840
Don't call me again.

138
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,720
There's nothing left to say.

139
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,320
Wait.

140
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:46,080
Congratulations on your comeback.

141
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:48,000
And...

142
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,080
I'm sorry.

143
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,550
Leslie?

144
00:12:27,510 --> 00:12:29,440
Who's that? Never heard of him.

145
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,510
And already an editor-in-chief?

146
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,080
Looks handsome.

147
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:35,670
Was he a model before?

148
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:37,550
Handsome? Where?

149
00:12:38,910 --> 00:12:40,150
And you call yourself a stylist?

150
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:41,270
You have no taste.

151
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,720
Better than you.

152
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:46,550
I'm taller.

153
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,270
I'm younger.

154
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:50,510
And I have more potential than him.

155
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:53,910
I meant my taste is better than yours.

156
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,550
What were you thinking?

157
00:13:00,630 --> 00:13:01,840
Talking nonsense.

158
00:13:15,380 --> 00:13:19,060
[Hailiwang Seafood]

159
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:27,360
Wait.

160
00:13:28,390 --> 00:13:30,750
Why are you comparing yourself to him?

161
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,000
Did he do something to you?

162
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,910
He has nothing to do with you.

163
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:37,630
Besides, he's the editor-in-chief.

164
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:39,910
You were invited as vendors.

165
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:41,080
You...

166
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:43,960
It's just a fashion magazine.

167
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,320
What's the big deal
about shooting a cover?

168
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,390
It'll shoot you to stardom.

169
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:50,440
Especially for a rookie like you.

170
00:13:56,390 --> 00:13:58,030
It's normal not to be selected.

171
00:13:58,030 --> 00:14:00,000
You can't be lucky every single time.

172
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,510
Don't be upset.

173
00:14:02,750 --> 00:14:04,480
Just treat it as an experience.

174
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:06,840
Tell me about it.

175
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:07,910
Who did you see?

176
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,120
Luna?

177
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:10,080
Ka?

178
00:14:10,670 --> 00:14:11,480
Dai Chengyi?

179
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:15,600
Wait, don't tell me
you don't know any of them.

180
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:17,870
Dai is one of my idols.

181
