No way.

187
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:32,320
They just ran into each other

188
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:34,030
right in front of everyone?

189
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:35,720
Oh my gosh.

190
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,030
This is straight out of a drama.

191
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:38,750
That's ancient history.

192
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,120
Why are you so worked up?

193
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:40,840
But...

194
00:14:41,030 --> 00:14:42,670
how did Han Yijing react?

195
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:44,200
Did she freeze on the spot?

196
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:46,120
She turned and left,

197
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,120
completely ignoring him.

198
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:50,080
She's obviously not over him.

199
00:14:50,790 --> 00:14:51,630
The more she avoids him,

200
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:53,270
the more it proves she cares.

201
00:14:59,510 --> 00:15:00,510
You don't know her.

202
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:02,670
You don't know women.

203
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:05,600
Women are good at saying
the opposite of what they feel,

204
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:07,440
especially when it comes to an ex.

205
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,600
The meaner a woman is,

206
00:15:09,670 --> 00:15:11,440
the more she's probably still in love.

207
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:15,840
Hold this.

208
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,270
So what does Liao Jinyuan look like?

209
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:23,790
Hello?

210
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:25,030
Why was he there?

211
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:26,000
Taking photos?

212
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,480
No, thanks. Not needed.

213
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:11,160
Go straight home when it's done.

214
00:17:12,110 --> 00:17:14,310
I've canceled the dinner for you.

215
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:17,160
It's just a meal, no big deal.

216
00:17:17,750 --> 00:17:19,200
So people don't keep thinking
I'm difficult.

217
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:21,510
Skip it.

218
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:22,920
With your current state...

219
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:24,270
Which is great.

220
00:17:24,350 --> 00:17:25,350
You saw it yourself.

221
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:27,960
You didn't sleep well
last night, did you?

222
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:35,790
I declined the cover shoot too.

223
00:17:37,030 --> 00:17:38,440
If anyone contacts you privately,

224
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:39,920
just say you don't know anything

225
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:40,640
and ignore them.

226
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:42,510
Why?

227
00:17:43,590 --> 00:17:44,960
Just because it's Liao Jinyuan?

228
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:46,550
I don't care who he is or what he wants.

229
00:17:46,550 --> 00:17:48,200
But I will not let him
get near you again.

230
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:49,480
You're underestimating me.

231
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:51,160
Then why did you leave early yesterday?

232
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,030
Because to you,

233
00:17:55,030 --> 00:17:56,960
he's not just Whim's editor-in-chief.

234
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,480
I reminded you before.

235
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:13,590
Let me make it clear again.

236
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,110
If you let yourself
get swayed by him again,

237
00:18:16,110 --> 00:18:17,310
I will leave you alone

238
00:18:17,550 --> 00:18:18,920
and won't meddle
in your life ever again.

239
00:18:19,750 --> 00:18:20,720
You can do whatever you want.

240
00:18:27,790 --> 00:18:28,830
I just don't get it.

241
00:18:28,830 --> 00:18:30,000
The wrong person is...

242
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:37,960
It's me.

243
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:39,110
Sorry.

244
00:18:39,110 --> 00:18:39,920
I forgot to knock.

245
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,830
You've probably heard about it.

246
00:18:49,270 --> 00:18:50,110
Think whatever you want.

247
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,240
Just don't ask me.

248
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:52,590
What else can I think?

249
00:18:53,030 --> 00:18:54,110
I'd run too.

250
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:55,030
It was terrifying.

251
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:57,030
See for yourself.

252
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:00,960
Already scared someone out of her mind.

253
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:02,510
Lucky you ran fast.

254
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:05,350
Stop drinking.

255
00:19:06,350 --> 00:19:07,030
Stop drinking.

256
00:19:07,030 --> 00:19:07,720
Let go!

257
00:19:28,790 --> 00:19:29,480
Don't worry.

258
00:19:29,750 --> 00:19:30,880
Everything online
has been taken care of.

259
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,880
We've also reached out
to everyone present.

260
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:34,750
But we can't really act

261
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:36,110
like nothing ever happened.

262
00:19:37,030 --> 00:19:37,790
So...

263
00:19:52,700 --> 00:19:54,980
[Release Agreement]

264
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:56,830
Ms. Ling is dead set on this.

265
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:59,030
But given the time
you've known each other,

266
00:19:59,350 --> 00:20:00,550
